headline: Cerence (CRNC) Q3 Earnings and Revenues Surpass Estimates
summary: Cerence (CRNC) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +126.47% and +15.40%, respectively, for the quarter ended June 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?

headline: JACK HENRY & ASSOCIATES TO PROVIDE WEBCAST OF FOURTH QUARTER FISCAL 2025 EARNINGS CALL
summary: Jack Henry & Associates, Inc.® (NASDAQ: JKHY) announced today that it will host a live Webcast of its fourth quarter and full fiscal year 2025 earnings conference call on August 20, 2025. The press release announcing fiscal 2025 earnings will be issued after market close on August 19, 2025.
